2. Use the modifications, assets, or source code introduced in this fork
   (including but not limited to 3D models, textures, UI elements, scripts,
   and game mechanics) for any commercial purpose, including:
   - Selling access to the game or modified versions.
   - Using assets in other monetized games or platforms.
   - Packaging or selling the code or content as part of another product
     or service.
3. Claim authorship of this fork or imply endorsement by either the original
   developers or the author of this fork.
4. Reuse any assets or modifications introduced in this fork (scripts, models,
   textures, audio, UI) outside of Underengineered without prior written
